WEBVTT

00:07.013 --> 00:09.513
<i>Previously on "Billions"...</i>

00:09.515 --> 00:11.481
- Cancer?
- Yeah.

00:11.483 --> 00:13.017
- Shit.
- Pancreatic.

00:13.019 --> 00:15.085
Walter and the kids gonna have enough?

00:15.087 --> 00:17.955
Nobody's gonna starve, but
I could've done better.

00:17.957 --> 00:19.389
Forty million.

00:19.391 --> 00:21.191
What if we could get you there?

00:21.193 --> 00:24.094
It won't be simple. It'll
require deception.

00:24.096 --> 00:25.595
<i>[Bobby] And your final weeks and months,</i>

00:25.597 --> 00:26.896
<i>they won't be your own.</i>

00:26.898 --> 00:29.533
Bobby Axelrod used Donnie
to feed us information

00:29.535 --> 00:32.936
that he would never live to testify to.

00:32.938 --> 00:35.238
<i>♪ tense music ♪</i>

00:35.240 --> 00:37.106
Donnie's gone.

00:37.108 --> 00:40.242
How long you figure it's been
since we've had a session?

00:40.244 --> 00:41.578
<i>[Lara] I made some decisions.</i>

00:41.580 --> 00:42.779
You shuttered it.

00:42.781 --> 00:44.447
<i>[Lara] Selling the farm, too.</i>

00:44.449 --> 00:45.682
<i>[Chuck Sr.] You know, if you had</i>

00:45.684 --> 00:46.950
<i>listened to me in the first place</i>

00:46.952 --> 00:48.484
<i>and hadn't blown up the
deal with Axelrod,</i>

00:48.486 --> 00:50.720
we would not be in this spot, would we?

00:50.722 --> 00:54.623
The game has changed, and you
haven't changed with it.

00:54.625 --> 00:57.226
Your advice is no longer welcome.

00:57.228 --> 01:00.896
It was hard on Donnie,

01:00.898 --> 01:02.565
not being able to tell you.

01:02.567 --> 01:04.467
Did other people know?

01:04.468 --> 01:06.635
Hey. What are you doing here?

01:06.637 --> 01:08.837
<i>[Ari] He is a candidate for
a drug trial in Pittsburgh</i>

01:08.839 --> 01:10.572
that's been yielding some
pretty interesting results.

01:10.574 --> 01:13.341
Kind of rough for a guy who's
been through a lot already.

01:13.343 --> 01:14.977
<i>[Ari] It can be.</i>

01:14.979 --> 01:16.712
<i>[Bobby] Maybe we shouldn't bring it up.</i>

